'''Requests'''是一个[[Python|Python]] HTTP[[函式库|库]]，在[[Apache许可证|Apache License 2.0 许可证]]下发行。这个项目的目标是使HTTP请求更简单，更[[易用性|人性化]]。Requests是没有默认包含在Python内的最流行的Python库之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://docs.python.org/3/library/urllib.request.html#module-urllib.request|title=urllib.request — Extensible library for opening URL|quote=The Requests package is recommended for a higher-level HTTP client interface.|access-date=2021-03-13|archive-date=2021-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210528212132/https://docs.python.org/3/library/urllib.request.html#module-urllib.request}}</ref>，因此有人建议将其默认随Python一起发布<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Beazly |first1=David |title=R is for replacement |journal=login |date=April 2012 |volume=37 |issue=2 |url=https://www.usenix.org/system/files/login/articles/beazley12-04.pdf |accessdate=16 May 2020 |archive-date=2017-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824125933/https://www.usenix.org/system/files/login/articles/beazley12-04.pdf }}</ref>。

== 示例代码 ==
<syntaxhighlight lang="pycon">
>>> import requests
>>> r = requests.get('https://httpbin.org/basic-auth/user/pass', auth=('user', 'pass'))
>>> r.status_code
200
>>> r.headers['content-type']
'application/json; charset=utf8'
>>> r.encoding
'utf-8'
>>> r.text
'{"authenticated": true, ...'
>>> r.json()
{'authenticated': True, ...}
</syntaxhighlight>

